1
00:00:20,770 --> 00:00:21,604
Hei.

2
00:00:22,105 --> 00:00:23,732
Awak buat apa lagi di sini?

3
00:00:24,691 --> 00:00:27,944
Maaf. Saya ingat awak kawan saya tadi.

4
00:00:28,028 --> 00:00:30,113
Marilah. Semua orang dah sampai.

5
00:00:32,949 --> 00:00:35,410
Kenapa dia pergi?

6
00:00:37,495 --> 00:00:38,621
Aku silap orangkah?

7
00:00:39,622 --> 00:00:42,584
Mi-rae!

8
00:00:43,168 --> 00:00:44,461
Cik Choi?

9
00:00:45,879 --> 00:00:47,672
<i>Su-ji, kawan universiti.</i>

10
00:00:47,756 --> 00:00:49,049
Apa?

11
00:00:49,883 --> 00:00:52,385
Kampus ini besar sangat.
Saya selalu sesat.

12
00:00:52,469 --> 00:00:55,138
Lepas keluar tandas,
saya dah tak nampak awak.

13
00:00:55,221 --> 00:00:56,056
Jom!

14
00:00:56,723 --> 00:00:57,557
Pergi mana?

15
00:00:57,640 --> 00:01:00,185
Apa? Tadi kita janji nak pergi sama-sama.

16
00:01:01,394 --> 00:01:02,479
Pergi sana.

17
00:01:05,315 --> 00:01:08,151
Dah sampai!

18
00:01:08,234 --> 00:01:10,779
- Menarik, bukan?
- "Pelajar baru"?

19
00:01:10,862 --> 00:01:12,530
SELAMAT DATANG PELAJAR BARU!

20
00:01:12,614 --> 00:01:15,158
<i>Jangan kata saya pelajar tahun satu?</i>

21
00:01:15,241 --> 00:01:16,409
Takkanlah.

22
00:01:16,493 --> 00:01:17,535
Yang ini berapa?

23
00:01:17,619 --> 00:01:18,536
MAJLIS PELAJAR

24
00:01:18,620 --> 00:01:21,206
Cantiknya. Saya nak satu, boleh?

25
00:01:21,706 --> 00:01:22,540
Terima kasih!

26
00:01:23,875 --> 00:01:25,001
- Hei!
- Tengok ini.

27
00:01:25,085 --> 00:01:26,169
Pelajar baru!

28
00:01:49,651 --> 00:01:51,319
<i>Mengarut betullah.</i>

29
00:01:57,784 --> 00:01:59,744
Jom pergi. Teruknya.

30
00:01:59,828 --> 00:02:01,454
Boleh kita jumpa lagi?

31
00:02:01,538 --> 00:02:02,413
Tak naklah.

32
00:02:02,497 --> 00:02:03,623
Bukan awaklah!

33
00:02:03,706 --> 00:02:04,749
Berambuslah!

34
00:02:05,750 --> 00:02:06,626
Mari singgah!

35
00:02:06,709 --> 00:02:08,002
Marilah. Seronok.

36
00:02:08,086 --> 00:02:09,546
Singgahlah sini.

37
00:02:09,629 --> 00:02:11,339
- Sini!
- Datanglah sini.

38
00:02:11,422 --> 00:02:15,009
- Singgahlah sekejap.
- Lihat aktiviti kami.

39
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:18,429
- Kami ada kamera.
- Cuba sepak!

40
00:02:18,513 --> 00:02:20,640
- Ambil gambar percuma!
- Percuma!

41
00:02:20,723 --> 00:02:23,143
Kenapa ramai beratur di sini, Cik Choi?

42
00:02:23,226 --> 00:02:24,227
Hei!

43
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:27,188
Janganlah panggil saya cik.
Peliklah bunyinya.

44
00:02:29,399 --> 00:02:32,277
Lain macam, bukan? Pelik betul!

45
00:02:33,653 --> 00:02:37,323
Mesti mereka nak dapatkan
tiket perlawanan <i>kumdo </i>hari ini.

46
00:02:37,407 --> 00:02:40,368
Di tandas tadi,
saya dengar tiket dah habis.

47
00:02:40,451 --> 00:02:42,787
Mereka cuba nasib agaknya.

48
00:02:42,871 --> 00:02:45,165
Popular betul kelab <i>kumdo</i>.

49
00:02:46,332 --> 00:02:49,419
Dengar kata bola dan hoki pun
tak popular begini.

50
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:51,588
PERLAWANAN PERSAHABATAN

51
00:02:51,671 --> 00:02:53,798
Biar betul! Awak dapat tiket?

52
00:02:53,882 --> 00:02:56,134
Mana awak dapat? Hebat gila!

53
00:02:56,217 --> 00:02:58,094
Saya patut tonton, bukan?

54
00:02:59,012 --> 00:03:00,388
Awak wajib pergi.

55
00:03:01,431 --> 00:03:02,432
Jom cepat.

56
00:03:02,515 --> 00:03:03,850
Tempatnya di sana.

57
00:03:22,535 --> 00:03:23,620
Dia dah sampai!

58
00:03:23,703 --> 00:03:25,330
HANSAE LAWAN KOSAN

59
00:03:26,706 --> 00:03:27,540
Apa halnya?

60
00:03:28,583 --> 00:03:30,543
Saya kata jangan berdiri di sini!

61
00:03:30,627 --> 00:03:31,961
Kenapa pula tak boleh?

62
00:03:32,045 --> 00:03:33,630
Kamu halang orang lainlah!

63
00:03:33,713 --> 00:03:35,632
- Kecohlah.
- Apa awak cakap?

64
00:03:36,257 --> 00:03:39,219
Mereka siapa? Ahli kelab peminat?

65
00:03:39,302 --> 00:03:40,136
Rasanya.

66
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:43,473
Perlawanan persahabatan <i>kumdo</i>
Hansae-Kosan akan bermula.

67
00:03:43,556 --> 00:03:46,559
Universiti Hansae!

68
00:03:46,643 --> 00:03:47,936
SAYANG EUN-HO

69
00:03:48,019 --> 00:03:51,606
Universiti Hansae!

70
00:03:51,689 --> 00:03:54,943
- Universiti Hansae!
- Universiti Kosan!

71
00:03:55,026 --> 00:03:55,860
Mula!

72
00:03:59,364 --> 00:04:01,241
Pukulan kepala!

73
00:04:20,426 --> 00:04:24,138
- Pemenang, Seo Eun-ho, Universiti Hansae.
- Eun-ho!

74
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:28,559
Seterusnya, Park Myeong-seong,
Universiti Hansae,

75
00:04:28,643 --> 00:04:31,729
menentang An Hong-mo, Universiti Kosan.

76
00:04:31,813 --> 00:04:33,564
Diminta kekal duduk.

77
00:04:48,454 --> 00:04:50,415
Segak betul!

78
00:04:50,498 --> 00:04:52,333
Hebatnya dia.

79
00:05:06,139 --> 00:05:09,976
<i>Tahniah, Seo Mi-rae,</i>
<i>atas pertemuan dengan calon kedua!</i>

80
00:05:20,403 --> 00:05:21,446
Saya dah agak.

81
00:05:22,238 --> 00:05:23,448
Awak orangnya.

82
00:05:30,038 --> 00:05:33,833
EPISOD 3
PENGENALAN KEPADA CINTA PERTAMA

83
00:05:37,003 --> 00:05:38,087
KELAB KUMDO HANSAE

84
00:05:38,171 --> 00:05:40,423
Kamu mendaftar sebab Eun-ho, ya?

85
00:05:40,506 --> 00:05:41,341
Taklah.

86
00:05:42,592 --> 00:05:45,178
Tak apa. Kami jadi ahli pun sebab dialah.

87
00:05:45,678 --> 00:05:48,598
- Kamu nak kenal dia lebih dekat?
- Ya!

88
00:05:49,557 --> 00:05:51,642
Jangan berani potong giliran kami.

89
00:05:56,939 --> 00:05:59,317
Popular sangatkah Seo Eun-ho?

90
00:06:00,109 --> 00:06:01,736
Mestilah dia popular.

91
00:06:01,819 --> 00:06:06,157
Saya jamin semua pelajar perempuan
harap dia sambung belajar

92
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:08,201
sampai jadi profesor di sini.

93
00:06:08,701 --> 00:06:11,162
Nasib baik program seni bina lima tahun.

94
00:06:11,245 --> 00:06:15,375
Dia bukan pelajar sukan?
Wah, seni bina. Mesti dia pandai.

95
00:06:15,958 --> 00:06:19,629
Eun-ho layak bangunkan negara,
bukan sekadar syarikat!

96
00:06:19,712 --> 00:06:21,172
Betul!

97
00:06:21,756 --> 00:06:25,009
<i>Jadi, pelajar lelaki paling popular</i>
<i>di kampus minat aku?</i>

98
00:06:26,677 --> 00:06:27,929
<i>Menarik juga plotnya.</i>

99
00:06:28,012 --> 00:06:30,014
- Kenapa awak ketawa?
- Apa?

100
00:06:32,683 --> 00:06:33,643
Tak ada apa-apa.

101
00:06:37,730 --> 00:06:38,940
Perkenalkan diri?

102
00:06:42,777 --> 00:06:46,072
<i>Saya Seo Mi-rae, pelajar tahun satu.</i>
<i>Tak sabarnya nak mula!</i>

103
00:06:55,623 --> 00:06:56,874
<i>Ini di mana pula?</i>

104
00:06:58,751 --> 00:07:00,044
Dia kacak betul.

105
00:07:00,128 --> 00:07:03,214
Baiklah, pelajar baru.
Ini kali pertama kita jumpa.

106
00:07:03,714 --> 00:07:04,549
Kenalkan diri.

107
00:07:04,632 --> 00:07:08,177
- Helo.
- Helo.

108
00:07:11,514 --> 00:07:12,598
Hei.

109
00:07:12,682 --> 00:07:14,475
Awak buat apa lagi di sini?

110
00:07:16,144 --> 00:07:18,312
<i>Ini perempuan yang aku nampak tadi.</i>

111
00:07:18,396 --> 00:07:21,149
Presiden kelab kita cantik, bukan?

112
00:07:22,984 --> 00:07:23,985
Cantik.

113
00:07:41,586 --> 00:07:45,214
<i>Kumdo </i>ialah sukan terbaik
untuk tubuh dan otak yang cergas.

114
00:07:45,298 --> 00:07:46,466
Kamu pasti seronok,

115
00:07:46,549 --> 00:07:50,178
bermula dengan belajar posisi asas
hinggalah sesi pertarungan.

116
00:07:50,678 --> 00:07:54,348
Ini baru hari pertama,
jadi kita mula dengan gerak kaki asas.

117
00:07:55,349 --> 00:07:56,601
Siapa nak tawar diri?

118
00:07:57,268 --> 00:07:58,686
Ada yang nak cuba?

119
00:08:07,487 --> 00:08:09,405
Bagus. Datang depan.

120
00:08:09,989 --> 00:08:10,823
Apa?

121
00:08:13,618 --> 00:08:14,744
Tak nak. Tak apa.

122
00:08:14,827 --> 00:08:16,204
Marilah. Jangan segan.

123
00:08:16,287 --> 00:08:17,163
Pergilah.

124
00:08:22,043 --> 00:08:23,377
Siapa nama awak?

125
00:08:23,461 --> 00:08:25,838
Seo Mi-rae.

126
00:08:32,386 --> 00:08:35,806
Bagus juga kalau ada orang sudi tolong.

127
00:08:38,351 --> 00:08:40,186
Okey. Boleh tolong kami?

128
00:08:40,269 --> 00:08:42,980
Mereka semua memang datang
nak tengok awak pun.

129
00:08:44,774 --> 00:08:45,608
Saya?

130
00:08:48,986 --> 00:08:50,780
Awak tak kisah, bukan?

131
00:08:51,989 --> 00:08:52,823
Tak kisah.

132
00:08:59,872 --> 00:09:00,706
Hai.

133
00:09:02,166 --> 00:09:03,668
Helo.

134
00:09:03,751 --> 00:09:05,294
Awak pernah cuba <i>kumdo</i>?

135
00:09:06,671 --> 00:09:07,838
Tak pernah.

136
00:09:13,261 --> 00:09:14,095
Nah.

137
00:09:16,931 --> 00:09:18,266
Pegang macam ini.

138
00:09:19,392 --> 00:09:20,935
Kaki kanan ke depan.

139
00:09:24,021 --> 00:09:25,481
Macam mana? Selesa?

140
00:09:26,732 --> 00:09:27,567
Selesa.

141
00:09:29,318 --> 00:09:30,403
Posisi tinggi.

142
00:09:32,238 --> 00:09:33,239
Pukulan kepala.

143
00:09:33,322 --> 00:09:35,032
Ini pula posisi tengah,

144
00:09:35,658 --> 00:09:37,326
posisi paling asas.

145
00:09:37,827 --> 00:09:38,869
Nak cuba?

146
00:09:40,204 --> 00:09:41,038
Okey.

147
00:09:47,253 --> 00:09:48,087
Mula.

148
00:09:50,506 --> 00:09:51,340
Pukulan kepala.

149
00:09:59,932 --> 00:10:01,225
Biar betul?

150
00:10:02,184 --> 00:10:03,811
Betulkah ini kali pertama?

151
00:10:03,894 --> 00:10:06,063
Ya, saya tak pernah cuba.

152
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:11,527
<i>Apa dah jadi?</i>
<i>Selalunya aku tak pandai bersukan.</i>

153
00:10:13,738 --> 00:10:17,033
Mesti awak pandai bersukan.
Mari cuba sekali lagi.

154
00:10:18,951 --> 00:10:19,785
Okey.

155
00:10:59,075 --> 00:11:02,495
Laju macam lipas kudung!
Macam tak percaya.

156
00:11:02,995 --> 00:11:04,288
Hebat.

157
00:11:04,789 --> 00:11:07,333
Awak ada bakat, Mi-rae.

158
00:11:07,416 --> 00:11:09,835
Mana ada, Eun-ho beri dia peluang.

159
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:10,878
Sebenarnya tak.

160
00:11:12,129 --> 00:11:13,547
Syabas.

161
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,258
Semoga dapat lawan lagi.

162
00:11:18,678 --> 00:11:19,512
Okey.

163
00:11:21,138 --> 00:11:23,182
- Pukulan kepala!
- Pukulan kepala.

164
00:11:23,265 --> 00:11:25,351
- Hebatnya dia.
- Satu.

165
00:11:25,851 --> 00:11:27,186
- Ya!
- Pukulan kepala.

166
00:11:27,269 --> 00:11:29,188
- Stabilnya dia.
- Posisi tengah.

167
00:11:29,271 --> 00:11:31,774
Dia memang abang sado!

168
00:11:31,857 --> 00:11:33,025
Betul!

169
00:11:33,818 --> 00:11:35,361
Macam berjalan. Tengok.

170
00:11:35,444 --> 00:11:36,320
Satu!

171
00:11:36,404 --> 00:11:37,405
Pukulan kepala!

172
00:11:38,239 --> 00:11:39,490
Bagus.

173
00:11:41,033 --> 00:11:42,410
En. Ko?

174
00:11:51,544 --> 00:11:54,463
Kenapa kamu berdiri saja?
Ada yang tak kena?

175
00:11:55,631 --> 00:11:57,341
<i>Jung-pil, senior kelab </i>kumdo<i>.</i>

176
00:11:58,008 --> 00:11:59,009
Sebenarnya…

177
00:11:59,885 --> 00:12:00,720
Nama awak?

178
00:12:02,179 --> 00:12:03,347
- Su-ji.
- Su-ji?

179
00:12:03,431 --> 00:12:04,807
- Ya.
- Mari, Su-ji.

180
00:12:04,890 --> 00:12:05,725
Okey.

181
00:12:06,350 --> 00:12:09,562
- Kunci <i>kumdo </i>ialah pergerakan lancar.
- Okey.

182
00:12:09,645 --> 00:12:10,771
Pukulan kepala!

183
00:12:11,522 --> 00:12:12,440
Pukulan kepala!

184
00:12:12,523 --> 00:12:14,233
Lancar betul.

185
00:12:14,316 --> 00:12:15,317
Awak cubalah.

186
00:12:17,361 --> 00:12:18,529
Pukulan kepala!

187
00:12:19,029 --> 00:12:20,906
Tolong tengokkan semua orang.

188
00:12:20,990 --> 00:12:22,158
Okey.

189
00:12:22,241 --> 00:12:23,492
Pukulan kepala!

190
00:12:27,747 --> 00:12:28,581
Eun-ho.

191
00:12:31,542 --> 00:12:34,378
- Awak nak ke mana?
- Perpustakaan. Kenapa?

192
00:12:35,838 --> 00:12:37,923
Awak nak makan dengan saya?

193
00:12:39,091 --> 00:12:40,050
Ramai-ramai?

194
00:12:41,761 --> 00:12:42,595
Tak.

195
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:44,930
Berdua saja?

196
00:12:45,598 --> 00:12:46,432
Ya.

197
00:12:49,810 --> 00:12:51,312
Awak tak sabar, ya?

198
00:12:52,980 --> 00:12:55,316
Lain kalilah, selepas kita lebih kenal.

199
00:12:56,192 --> 00:12:57,610
- Apa?
- Jaga diri.

200
00:12:59,236 --> 00:13:00,863
Eun-ho?

201
00:13:00,946 --> 00:13:02,031
Hei, Eun-ho!

202
00:13:03,532 --> 00:13:05,201
Pergi mana? Saya nak ikut.

203
00:13:05,284 --> 00:13:06,202
Jom makan.

204
00:13:11,415 --> 00:13:13,417
Kau patut jatuh cinta dengan aku!

205
00:13:13,501 --> 00:13:14,877
<i>Kenapa pula?</i>

206
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:18,005
Dia kena suka saya.
Namanya pun Boyfriend on Demand.

207
00:13:18,506 --> 00:13:21,425
Saya rasa awak dah salah faham.

208
00:13:21,509 --> 00:13:22,343
Salah faham?

209
00:13:23,302 --> 00:13:27,807
Awak ingat semua 900 lelaki di sini
akan kejar awak dari awal?

210
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:31,268
Tapi…

211
00:13:35,147 --> 00:13:36,774
Choi Si-woo suka saya dari…

212
00:13:36,857 --> 00:13:40,152
Senario untuk dia memang ditulis begitu.

213
00:13:43,781 --> 00:13:46,992
Sekali pandang,
saya tak sangka awak kuat perasan.

214
00:13:47,827 --> 00:13:51,539
Maksudnya, Seo Eun-ho
mungkin takkan jatuh cinta kepada saya?

215
00:13:51,622 --> 00:13:53,541
Susah nak cakap.

216
00:13:53,624 --> 00:13:55,543
Ada calon yang lebih cerewet.

217
00:13:56,252 --> 00:13:59,839
Kalau saya perlu berusaha,
apa bezanya dengan realiti?

218
00:13:59,922 --> 00:14:03,259
Awak nak tukar lelaki?
Nak cari calon lain pula?

219
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:09,265
Jangan, tunggulah. Hei!

220
00:14:09,348 --> 00:14:10,349
Tunggu dulu.

221
00:14:10,432 --> 00:14:13,769
Kalau tak berkenan, tukar sajalah.
Masa dah suntuk.

222
00:14:13,853 --> 00:14:15,771
Saya tahu. Masa dah…

223
00:14:16,772 --> 00:14:17,606
Masa?

224
00:14:29,994 --> 00:14:30,828
Terkejut aku.

225
00:14:44,091 --> 00:14:45,259
Kyeong-nam.

226
00:14:46,635 --> 00:14:47,636
Tengoklah dia.

227
00:14:51,473 --> 00:14:52,308
Awak nak kopi?

228
00:14:52,391 --> 00:14:55,185
Episod pertama <i>PlanC </i>pun boleh tahan.

229
00:15:00,566 --> 00:15:01,984
Tapi susah nak lawan Yun Song.

230
00:15:03,235 --> 00:15:04,737
Saya dah tahu dari awal.

231
00:15:05,321 --> 00:15:07,990
Betulkah awak minta tukar
kepada hari Jumaat?

232
00:15:08,073 --> 00:15:08,908
Tak.

233
00:15:10,534 --> 00:15:11,994
Cik Seo tak percaya.

234
00:15:12,578 --> 00:15:14,830
Memanglah. Dia tak suka saya.

235
00:15:16,415 --> 00:15:17,875
Macamlah awak suka dia.

236
00:15:27,509 --> 00:15:28,344
Apa?

237
00:15:29,887 --> 00:15:30,846
Ya?

238
00:15:32,556 --> 00:15:33,390
Masuklah.

239
00:15:37,770 --> 00:15:39,229
Bos nak jumpa saya?

240
00:15:40,981 --> 00:15:42,900
Yun Song baru telefon.

241
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:44,860
Apa? Dia nak apa?

242
00:15:44,944 --> 00:15:48,030
Perempuan itu nak apa lagi
kalau telefon saya?

243
00:15:49,615 --> 00:15:51,742
Saya nak tamatkan siri ini.

244
00:15:51,825 --> 00:15:53,369
Saya dah penat dan meluat!

245
00:15:53,452 --> 00:15:55,871
Tolonglah selamatkan saya.

246
00:15:59,917 --> 00:16:03,003
Jangan kata dia terfikir nak berhenti?

247
00:16:03,087 --> 00:16:04,630
- Dia nak berhenti?
- Apa?

248
00:16:04,713 --> 00:16:06,423
- Apa?
- Taklah.

249
00:16:06,507 --> 00:16:07,466
Peninglah.

250
00:16:08,175 --> 00:16:09,259
Habis, kenapa dia…

251
00:16:10,469 --> 00:16:13,931
Dia nak cuti dua minggu.
Kalau tak dapat, dia kata dia nak mati.

252
00:16:14,765 --> 00:16:17,226
Dia lalui macam-macam akhir-akhir ini.

253
00:16:18,769 --> 00:16:19,603
Awak bagus.

254
00:16:20,938 --> 00:16:23,565
- Apa?
- Saya suka. Teruskan usaha.

255
00:16:24,274 --> 00:16:27,069
- Saya tak faham kenapa awak merungut.
- Taklah…

256
00:16:27,152 --> 00:16:30,322
Sementara Yun bercuti,
fikirkan episod seterusnya.

257
00:16:31,991 --> 00:16:34,076
Bos beri dia cuti?

258
00:16:35,828 --> 00:16:37,496
Hari kerja pun boleh lepak?

259
00:16:37,579 --> 00:16:39,415
Sedap betul baunya. Cepat.

260
00:16:41,250 --> 00:16:45,254
Jadi, dua minggulah awak tak sibuk.
Nak ke Jeju hujung minggu ini?

261
00:16:45,337 --> 00:16:47,464
Jeju? Jangan haraplah.

262
00:16:47,548 --> 00:16:49,883
Saya perlu uruskan penulis lain.

263
00:16:51,176 --> 00:16:55,139
Jadi penerbit memang tak berbaloi.

264
00:16:55,222 --> 00:16:56,515
Memang pun!

265
00:16:57,349 --> 00:16:59,268
Ini nampak sedap betul!

266
00:17:01,645 --> 00:17:02,479
Hei, Ji-yeon.

267
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:08,318
Kalau awak boleh jadi 20 tahun semula,
awak nak cuba buat apa?

268
00:17:12,948 --> 00:17:13,782
Seks.

269
00:17:16,326 --> 00:17:17,536
Bukan benda begitu!

270
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:22,708
Kenapa tiba-tiba tanya?
Kalau awak, awak nak buat apa?

271
00:17:24,376 --> 00:17:29,048
Saya nak hidup saya berbeza,
berlawanan dengan hidup sekarang.

272
00:17:29,131 --> 00:17:31,091
- Berlawanan?
- Ya.

273
00:17:31,175 --> 00:17:34,928
Kalau saya jatuh cinta,
saya takkan malu-malu nak memikat.

274
00:17:35,012 --> 00:17:36,388
Walau apa pun berlaku,

275
00:17:37,014 --> 00:17:41,101
saya akan bertindak dan kawal keadaan.

276
00:17:43,729 --> 00:17:46,565
Janganlah buat saya gelak!

277
00:17:46,648 --> 00:17:47,733
Apa yang lawaknya?

278
00:17:47,816 --> 00:17:51,028
Dulu memang awak yang kawal keadaan.

279
00:17:51,111 --> 00:17:51,987
Betulkah?

280
00:17:52,071 --> 00:17:53,155
Betul!

281
00:17:54,656 --> 00:17:56,825
Se-june suka You-mi,

282
00:17:56,909 --> 00:18:00,329
tapi awak gigih mengurat dia
sampai dia jadi milik awak.

283
00:18:01,914 --> 00:18:03,916
Awak dah lupa, ya?

284
00:18:05,292 --> 00:18:08,378
Dulu You-mi budak popular.

285
00:18:09,129 --> 00:18:11,340
Tapi saya lebih popularlah.

286
00:18:13,509 --> 00:18:16,303
Betul cakap awak. Saya memang begitu.

287
00:18:19,723 --> 00:18:21,391
Macam mana saya jadi begini?

288
00:18:22,434 --> 00:18:25,604
Saya rasa awak berubah
sebab bercinta lama sangat.

289
00:18:26,188 --> 00:18:27,856
Usia pun satu faktor.

290
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:29,233
Saya rasa

291
00:18:30,025 --> 00:18:32,611
hubungan kami sangat bahagia pada mulanya.

292
00:18:34,446 --> 00:18:36,198
Ya, saya setuju.

293
00:18:36,740 --> 00:18:38,450
Saya cemburukan kamu dulu.

294
00:18:47,209 --> 00:18:49,169
<i>Seo Eun-ho</i>

295
00:18:49,670 --> 00:18:51,463
<i>bukan sasaran yang mudah.</i>

296
00:18:53,173 --> 00:18:56,718
<i>Dulu memang awak yang kawal keadaan.</i>

297
00:18:59,596 --> 00:19:01,098
Patutkah saya cuba?

298
00:19:01,598 --> 00:19:03,934
Kuil dalam seni bina klasik

299
00:19:04,017 --> 00:19:08,272
dikategorikan mengikut bilangan tiang
di depan dan belakang bangunan.

300
00:19:09,064 --> 00:19:11,567
Ia dipanggil <i>"distyle" </i>jika ada dua tiang,

301
00:19:11,650 --> 00:19:16,780
<i>"tetrastyle" </i>jika ada empat tiang
dan <i>"hexastyle" </i>jika ada enam tiang.

302
00:19:17,281 --> 00:19:18,907
Berkenaan <i>"hexastyle"</i>…

303
00:19:31,837 --> 00:19:32,921
Helo.

304
00:19:33,422 --> 00:19:34,256
Hai.

305
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:37,259
- Boleh saya duduk sini?
- Duduklah.

306
00:19:41,930 --> 00:19:42,764
Tepi sikit.

307
00:19:43,682 --> 00:19:44,766
Sekejap.

308
00:19:54,318 --> 00:19:55,569
Silakan lalu.

309
00:19:59,448 --> 00:20:01,325
Nak jual mahal, ya?

310
00:20:03,202 --> 00:20:06,538
Tiang kuil boleh dikategorikan
mengikut bentuknya…

311
00:20:06,622 --> 00:20:12,127
<i>Aku nekad nak mengurat sampai dapat,</i>
<i>jadi aku keluarkan semua taktik lama.</i>

312
00:20:15,756 --> 00:20:17,049
Dah sampai mana?

313
00:20:26,183 --> 00:20:27,643
Terima kasih!

314
00:20:39,446 --> 00:20:40,405
Maaflah tadi.

315
00:20:52,918 --> 00:20:53,752
Hei.

316
00:20:56,463 --> 00:20:57,297
Ya?

317
00:20:58,090 --> 00:20:59,466
Awak tak sihatkah?

318
00:21:02,511 --> 00:21:03,345
Sihat saja.

319
00:21:04,012 --> 00:21:04,846
Okey.

320
00:21:05,597 --> 00:21:07,140
Jom fokus pada kuliah, ya?

321
00:21:19,820 --> 00:21:22,114
Eun-ho, awak nak pergi latihan <i>kumdo</i>?

322
00:21:22,614 --> 00:21:23,782
Tak, perpustakaan.

323
00:21:25,075 --> 00:21:27,077
Bagus, saya pun nak ke sana.

324
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:28,954
Sebenarnya, saya ada latihan.

325
00:21:30,789 --> 00:21:32,582
Samalah. Saya pun ada latihan.

326
00:22:00,068 --> 00:22:01,403
Nak mula dulu?

327
00:22:30,390 --> 00:22:31,308
<i>Dia buat apa?</i>

328
00:22:33,518 --> 00:22:34,436
<i>Wah!</i>

329
00:22:35,437 --> 00:22:36,563
<i>Dia suka akukah?</i>

330
00:22:54,122 --> 00:22:55,374
Kali ini…

331
00:22:58,919 --> 00:23:00,295
jangan beri saya peluang.

332
00:23:05,050 --> 00:23:06,385
Lawan habis-habisan.

333
00:23:07,928 --> 00:23:08,762
<i>Alamak.</i>

334
00:23:11,973 --> 00:23:12,974
Pakai.

335
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:22,984
<i>Aku dah calarkan ego dia.</i>

336
00:23:34,538 --> 00:23:36,039
Mi-rae, hai!

337
00:23:36,123 --> 00:23:37,666
Helo.

338
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:40,001
Apa dah jadi?

339
00:23:40,669 --> 00:23:42,379
Kamu berdua bertarungkah?

340
00:23:43,672 --> 00:23:45,757
Sebenarnya,

341
00:23:46,258 --> 00:23:47,175
Eun-ho…

342
00:23:47,259 --> 00:23:48,468
Saya yang cadangkan.

343
00:23:53,306 --> 00:23:56,393
Habis? Apa yang jadi?

344
00:24:00,272 --> 00:24:02,315
MI-RAE, EUN-HO

345
00:24:02,399 --> 00:24:04,359
<i>Aku patut jadi ratu kampus.</i>

346
00:24:04,443 --> 00:24:07,070
<i>Kenapa aku jadi jaguh pedang pula?</i>

347
00:24:07,154 --> 00:24:08,280
MENANG, KALAH

348
00:24:10,157 --> 00:24:11,366
Biar betul.

349
00:24:11,867 --> 00:24:13,160
Awak kalah?

350
00:24:16,163 --> 00:24:17,497
Saya tak percayalah.

351
00:24:18,498 --> 00:24:19,332
Betulkah?

352
00:24:22,711 --> 00:24:24,129
Saya nak mandi.

353
00:24:36,266 --> 00:24:38,477
Ayuh!

354
00:24:38,977 --> 00:24:41,354
Umchichi, umchichi!

355
00:24:41,438 --> 00:24:43,648
- Arnab, arnab!
- Lobak, lobak!

356
00:24:44,232 --> 00:24:48,069
<i>Dah lama aku tak rasa seronok</i>
<i>dan bertenaga macam orang muda!</i>

357
00:24:48,153 --> 00:24:49,154
Lobak, lobak!

358
00:24:49,237 --> 00:24:50,697
Arnab, arnab!

359
00:24:50,780 --> 00:24:55,368
- Arnab, arnab!
- Arnab, arnab!

360
00:24:55,452 --> 00:24:57,954
Awak tersilap, Jung-pil! Minum!

361
00:24:58,538 --> 00:24:59,956
Minum!

362
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:01,041
Saya nak…

363
00:25:02,209 --> 00:25:03,210
minum untuk dia.

364
00:25:05,128 --> 00:25:07,714
- Hei! Siapkan minuman denda!
- Denda!

365
00:25:07,797 --> 00:25:08,798
Okey!

366
00:25:09,508 --> 00:25:10,675
Biar saya bancuh.

367
00:25:10,759 --> 00:25:11,635
Mi-rae!

368
00:25:11,718 --> 00:25:13,762
- Mi-rae!
- Okey, bancuh.

369
00:25:16,389 --> 00:25:17,432
Sedia.

370
00:25:20,810 --> 00:25:21,978
Masuk <i>soju </i>sekali?

371
00:25:28,193 --> 00:25:30,445
Nah, minuman denda.

372
00:25:31,821 --> 00:25:33,615
Mi-rae…

373
00:25:35,158 --> 00:25:37,202
awak macam berpengalaman betul.

374
00:25:37,285 --> 00:25:40,205
<i>Aku terbawa-bawa pula.</i>

375
00:25:40,288 --> 00:25:41,706
Betulkah cara saya buat?

376
00:25:42,332 --> 00:25:43,583
Eun-ho!

377
00:25:43,667 --> 00:25:44,960
- Helo, Eun-ho.
- Hei!

378
00:25:45,043 --> 00:25:46,586
- Hai, Eun-ho.
- Duduklah.

379
00:25:47,796 --> 00:25:49,881
- Duduk sini.
- Helo, Eun-ho.

380
00:25:50,507 --> 00:25:52,050
Kenapa lambat sangat?

381
00:25:52,133 --> 00:25:53,343
- Ada tugasan.
- Minum.

382
00:25:53,426 --> 00:25:55,512
Minum! Jom!

383
00:25:57,097 --> 00:25:58,265
Su-ji, cukuplah.

384
00:25:59,432 --> 00:26:02,143
Tak apa. Saya tahu awak cepat mabuk.

385
00:26:02,227 --> 00:26:03,228
Minum.

386
00:26:03,311 --> 00:26:04,563
Biar saya minum.

387
00:26:05,772 --> 00:26:09,234
<i>Aku memang berbulu tengok</i>
<i>perempuan itu dari awal lagi.</i>

388
00:26:09,734 --> 00:26:11,903
<i>Gaya dia ala-ala Na You-mi.</i>

389
00:26:12,404 --> 00:26:13,697
Ada benda melekat.

390
00:26:14,864 --> 00:26:15,699
Jung-pil!

391
00:26:16,491 --> 00:26:18,285
Janganlah paksa diri!

392
00:26:18,785 --> 00:26:20,704
Mesti awak rasa teruk esok.

393
00:26:21,788 --> 00:26:24,708
Mi-rae, awak pernah main sukan apa-apa?

394
00:26:26,418 --> 00:26:27,502
Tak pernah.

395
00:26:28,628 --> 00:26:30,046
Awak pelajar seni.

396
00:26:30,130 --> 00:26:33,550
Artis berbakat dan atlet handalan.
Orang kata, serba boleh!

397
00:26:35,677 --> 00:26:38,430
Janganlah puji lebih-lebih.

398
00:26:41,099 --> 00:26:43,143
Rendah diri sangat pun tak elok.

399
00:26:44,561 --> 00:26:46,021
Mengarut saja.

400
00:26:46,521 --> 00:26:48,148
Merendah diri itu bagus.

401
00:26:48,648 --> 00:26:50,275
Tapi betullah kata Eun-ho.

402
00:26:50,358 --> 00:26:53,945
Saya meluat juga tengok orang
yang terlalu merendah diri.

403
00:26:54,029 --> 00:26:54,863
Betul.

404
00:26:56,239 --> 00:26:57,324
Hei.

405
00:26:57,949 --> 00:26:58,992
Apa?

406
00:26:59,075 --> 00:26:59,993
Bukan awaklah.

407
00:27:03,496 --> 00:27:04,497
Awak benci saya?

408
00:27:07,042 --> 00:27:07,876
Apa?

409
00:27:12,505 --> 00:27:14,049
Saya tak benci orang.

410
00:27:15,717 --> 00:27:17,385
Kalau awak terasa, maaflah.

411
00:27:21,348 --> 00:27:22,474
Baguslah.

412
00:27:24,476 --> 00:27:26,144
- Mi-rae?
- Mi-rae.

413
00:27:26,227 --> 00:27:27,687
Awak nak ke mana?

414
00:27:34,402 --> 00:27:36,821
Sebab saya suka awak, Eun-ho.

415
00:27:38,865 --> 00:27:40,825
- Apa?
- Saya rasa dia mabuk!

416
00:27:40,909 --> 00:27:43,620
- Wah!
- Jangan potong giliran, Mi-rae!

417
00:27:48,625 --> 00:27:50,460
Tapi kita baru jumpa.

418
00:27:51,294 --> 00:27:52,128
Apa?

419
00:27:53,213 --> 00:27:54,923
Awak tak kenal saya pun.

420
00:28:01,429 --> 00:28:04,015
Budak sekarang memang berani, betul tak?

421
00:28:04,099 --> 00:28:06,434
Jung-pil, muka awak comot.

422
00:28:06,518 --> 00:28:07,769
Alamak, malunya.

423
00:28:07,852 --> 00:28:08,853
Comot pun kacak.

424
00:28:09,979 --> 00:28:11,106
- Comel.
- Dia gilakah?

425
00:28:11,189 --> 00:28:12,315
Sekejap.

426
00:28:13,108 --> 00:28:13,942
- Minum.
- Jom.

427
00:28:14,025 --> 00:28:15,860
- Bagus, Jung-pil!
- Nah!

428
00:28:18,363 --> 00:28:19,406
<i>Apa dah jadi?</i>

429
00:28:19,489 --> 00:28:20,657
Awak memang hebat.

430
00:28:20,740 --> 00:28:22,200
- Jumpa lagi.
- Balik dulu!

431
00:28:22,283 --> 00:28:24,035
- Awak nak naik?
- Boleh?

432
00:28:24,119 --> 00:28:25,203
Ya. Masuklah.

433
00:28:25,787 --> 00:28:27,122
Terima kasih.

434
00:28:27,205 --> 00:28:28,707
Marilah naik sekali.

435
00:28:49,310 --> 00:28:50,186
Nak ke mana?

436
00:28:51,062 --> 00:28:51,938
Balik kampus.

437
00:28:53,356 --> 00:28:54,858
Awak tinggal di asrama?

438
00:28:56,359 --> 00:28:57,819
Awak nak ke kampus juga?

439
00:28:57,902 --> 00:29:00,947
Ya, saya nak siapkan tugasan
di perpustakaan.

440
00:29:09,706 --> 00:29:11,666
Jalan sajalah di sebelah saya.

441
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:13,918
Saya tak nak rasa macam kena kejar.

442
00:29:21,926 --> 00:29:23,595
- Eun-ho.
- Apa?

443
00:29:24,929 --> 00:29:26,431
Awak minat presiden kelab kita?

444
00:29:27,474 --> 00:29:28,308
Apa?

445
00:29:31,019 --> 00:29:33,104
Saya tak patut terus tanya begitu.

446
00:29:33,730 --> 00:29:35,482
Okey, awak asal dari mana?

447
00:29:35,565 --> 00:29:38,777
Awak minat orang macam mana?
Awak suka permainan video?

448
00:29:38,860 --> 00:29:39,694
Awak kenapa?

449
00:29:41,112 --> 00:29:44,741
Awak kata saya tak kenal awak.
Saya nak kenal cepat-cepatlah.

450
00:29:55,084 --> 00:29:55,919
Eun-ho!

451
00:29:59,672 --> 00:30:00,757
Lari!

452
00:30:58,648 --> 00:31:00,942
Mana boleh masuk kalau basah kuyup?

453
00:31:01,025 --> 00:31:03,236
Saya bawa baju kering.

454
00:31:03,945 --> 00:31:05,613
Keringkanlah baju dulu.

455
00:31:09,659 --> 00:31:10,577
KOLEJ KEDIAMAN

456
00:31:10,660 --> 00:31:11,578
BILIK DOBI

457
00:31:13,204 --> 00:31:14,747
<i>Amboi, ada bantuan!</i>

458
00:31:15,790 --> 00:31:17,542
Sekejap lagi keringlah.

459
00:31:18,585 --> 00:31:19,669
Jaga diri.

460
00:31:19,752 --> 00:31:20,837
Tunggu dulu!

461
00:31:23,214 --> 00:31:25,633
Ada cara untuk keringkan baju.

462
00:31:42,817 --> 00:31:44,903
Terima kasih benarkan saya guna dobi.

463
00:31:45,737 --> 00:31:47,739
Lama juga nak siap, bukan?

464
00:31:48,781 --> 00:31:49,699
Lama juga.

465
00:31:53,953 --> 00:31:55,496
Awak pun patut tukar baju.

466
00:31:59,375 --> 00:32:00,460
Tak nak.

467
00:32:02,545 --> 00:32:05,048
Saya nak temankan awak, Eun-ho.

468
00:32:13,932 --> 00:32:15,183
Awak memang pelik.

469
00:32:20,229 --> 00:32:21,814
Awak berani lain macam.

470
00:32:34,744 --> 00:32:37,747
<i>Ini yang aku tak jangka langsung.</i>

471
00:32:42,001 --> 00:32:42,961
Se-june.

472
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:45,713
Nah. Makanlah.

473
00:32:48,341 --> 00:32:50,885
Mi-rae, kenapa awak berani sangat?

474
00:32:51,719 --> 00:32:52,553
Apa saya buat?

475
00:32:54,347 --> 00:32:55,556
Awak suka saya?

476
00:32:56,516 --> 00:32:57,350
Ya.

477
00:33:12,198 --> 00:33:13,408
<i>Kenapa aku tiba-tiba</i>

478
00:33:14,200 --> 00:33:16,244
<i>teringat si bodoh ini?</i>

479
00:33:58,494 --> 00:33:59,454
Eun-ho.

480
00:34:25,104 --> 00:34:26,856
Nanti awak demam pula.

481
00:34:28,066 --> 00:34:29,317
Keringkan rambut.

482
00:34:33,821 --> 00:34:35,406
Saya tak minat dia, okey?

483
00:34:40,995 --> 00:34:43,915
Sementara tunggu baju,
saya nak ke bilik bacaan. Jumpa lagi.

484
00:34:44,999 --> 00:34:46,167
Tunggu…

485
00:34:46,751 --> 00:34:48,044
Jangan demam.

486
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:14,737
Apa bendalah pula? Kacau betul.

487
00:35:26,999 --> 00:35:30,002
<i>Mem Besar suruh letak</i>
<i>gambar dia yang lawa saja.</i>

